心。 希望市府以「主動推動」的態度回應居民需求， 讓龜山林口居民不只住得下，更能生活得好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"辦法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望市府能“主動積極” 參考林口成功案例。 因應 A7 重劃區 各項生活機能都不足的狀況下, 發揮整合力量規劃綜合性現代化市場。 能將零售超市, 餐飲廣場, 公共托育, 圖書/閱覽室, 停車場及里民活動中心 等整合開發。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 新增的四個里, "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果能整合開發能同時解決 沒有里民活動中心的問題！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請參考下面林口的 公有市場 具備的多功能設施"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-04.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-04.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-06.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-06.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n麗林 托育中心"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-05.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-05.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n麗林 羽球館"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-07.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-07.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n林口公有市場的圖書館"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-09.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-09.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n林口 整潔的零售市場"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r045-10.png","src":"/images/resident/r045-10.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n林口 綠色建築與休閒區"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"a7-公有零售市場-建議案","depth":2,"text":"A7 公有零售市場, 建議案","children":[{"id":"主旨","depth":3,"text":"主旨"},{"id":"說明","depth":3,"text":"說明"},{"id":"辦法","depth":3,"text":"辦法"}]}]}},"_type